# FastAPI Development

Build high-performance APIs with FastAPI. Use Pydantic models for request/response validation, dependency injection for shared logic, and async handlers for I/O-bound endpoints.

## Structure
- `app/` - application package
  - `api/` - route handlers
  - `models/` - database models
  - `schemas/` - Pydantic schemas
  - `services/` - business logic
  - `core/` - config, dependencies, middleware
